swDlmsMIB.description: The D-Link License Management System module

swDlmsInstallAc.name: swDlmsInstallAc
swDlmsInstallAc.description: This object is used to install an activation code. swDlmsInstallStackUnitId, to be used to specify the unit ID when performing an AC installation.

swDlmsInstallStackUnitId.name: swDlmsInstallStackUnitId
swDlmsInstallStackUnitId.description: Specifies which unit of the switch stack the activation code will be installed. If the ID equals zero, it means the current device.

swDlmsLicenseModelTable.name: swDlmsLicenseModelTable
swDlmsLicenseModelTable.description: This table indicates license model. The table is for non-stackable device.

swDlmsLicenseModelName.name: swDlmsLicenseModelName
swDlmsLicenseModelName.description: This object indicates the license model name.

swDlmsLicenseModelRemaining.name: swDlmsLicenseModelRemaining
swDlmsLicenseModelRemaining.description: This object indicates the license remaining time.

swDlmsLicenseAcTable.name: swDlmsLicenseAcTable
swDlmsLicenseAcTable.description: This table lists activation codes. The table is for non-stackable device.

swDlmsLicenseAcEntry.name: swDlmsLicenseAcEntry
swDlmsLicenseAcEntry.description: A list of information indicates a activation code.

swDlmsLicenseAc.name: swDlmsLicenseAc
swDlmsLicenseAc.description: This object indicates the activation code.

swDlmsLicenseAcStatus.name: swDlmsLicenseAcStatus
swDlmsLicenseAcStatus.description: This object indicates the AC status.

swDlmsStackLicenseModelTable.name: swDlmsStackLicenseModelTable
swDlmsStackLicenseModelTable.description: This table indicates information about license models of devices stacked with the current device. The table is for stackable device.

swDlmsStackLicenseModelEntry.name: swDlmsStackLicenseModelEntry
swDlmsStackLicenseModelEntry.description: A list of information about each license model of devices stacked with this device.

swDlmsStackLicenseModelUnitId.name: swDlmsStackLicenseModelUnitId
swDlmsStackLicenseModelUnitId.description: Specifies which unit of the switch stack. If the ID equals zero, it means the current device.

swDlmsStackLicenseModelName.name: swDlmsStackLicenseModelName
swDlmsStackLicenseModelName.description: This object indicates the license model name.

swDlmsStackLicenseModelRemaining.name: swDlmsStackLicenseModelRemaining
swDlmsStackLicenseModelRemaining.description: This object indicates the license remaining time.

swDlmsStackLicenseAcTable.name: swDlmsStackLicenseAcTable
swDlmsStackLicenseAcTable.description: This table indicates information about activation codes of devices stacked with the current device. The table is for stackable device.

swDlmsStackLicenseAcEntry.name: swDlmsStackLicenseAcEntry
swDlmsStackLicenseAcEntry.description: A list of information about each activation code of devices stacked with this device.

swDlmsStackLicenseAc.name: swDlmsStackLicenseAc
swDlmsStackLicenseAc.description: This object indicates the activation code.

swDlmsStackLicenseAcStatus.name: swDlmsStackLicenseAcStatus
swDlmsStackLicenseAcStatus.description: This object indicates the AC status.

swDlmsIllegalAc.name: swDlmsIllegalAc
swDlmsIllegalAc.description: Generated when the user inputs an illegal activation code.

swDlmsLicenseExpired.name: swDlmsLicenseExpired
swDlmsLicenseExpired.description: The notification is sent when a license of non-stackable device is expired.

swDlmsLicenseInstallationSuccess.name: swDlmsLicenseInstallationSuccess
swDlmsLicenseInstallationSuccess.description: The notification is sent when a license of non-stackable device was installed successfully.

swDlmsLicenseExpiresIn30Days.name: swDlmsLicenseExpiresIn30Days
swDlmsLicenseExpiresIn30Days.description: When a license of non-stackable device is going to expire, the notification is sent before 30 days.

swDlmsStackLicenseExpired.name: swDlmsStackLicenseExpired
swDlmsStackLicenseExpired.description: The notification is sent when a license of devices stacked is expired.

swDlmsStackLicenseInstallationSuccess.description: The notification is sent when a license of devices stacked was installed successfully.

swDlmsStackLicenseExpiresIn30Days.description: When a license of devices stacked is going to expire, the notification is sent before 30 days.
